guardians.model.entities

Class Schedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • guardians.model.entities.Schedule

  • @Entity
 @ValidSchedule
public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object
    The Schedule Entity represents the scheduled shifts of a specific Calendar Note the primary key of this entity is composite, hence the IdClass annotation. Moreover, this is a weak entity, so it receives its primary key from the Calendar it is associated to
    Author:
    miggoncan
